  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb \u0dc4\u0dad\u0dbb\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0d9a \u0daf\u0da9\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A fine of five lakhs for four eggs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Balangoda Acting Magistrate A. to pay a fine of five lakh rupees to a business place in Balangoda town that sold eggs at a higher price than the prescribed price. Amy. S. Mrs. Menike ordered.",
        "This trading company was fined for selling 4 white eggs at a price of 260 rupees.",
        "The officials of the consumer authority said that the eggs were bought from the relevant market by a strategist and a sum of 260 rupees was charged for four eggs at 65 rupees per egg.",
        "Balangoda Acting Magistrate A.M.S. Mrs. Menike fixed the fine amount of five lakhs as follows.",
        "Officers Nasik Ahmed and Nadisha Liyanage were present for this raid which was organized by the investigation officer Mrs. Harshani Dasanayake on the instructions of Mr. Udaya Namalgama, District Head of Ratnapura Consumer Authority."
      ],
